snippet.title: ANNOUNCEMENT
snippet.description:
Super Smash Flash 2 is a non-profit fan project. Please support the developers of official titles!

Join our communities:
http://facebook.com/McLeodGaming
http://forums.mcleodgaming.com
https://twitter.com/mcleodgaming

Play Super Smash Flash 2:
http://tinyurl.com/playSSF2 (sorry about the typo!)

Apply to be a Super Smash Flash 2 Developer:
http://tinyurl.com/SSF2Apply

Press? Fire us an e-mail:
ssf2devs@mcleodgaming.com
